{"type": "article", "id": 29833, "title": "从这些彩色的秋千里穿过，会不会让你回忆起童年", "description": "这是卢森堡每年夏天的例行项目，策划者希望将人群重新聚集到市中心。", "date": "2016-07-19T23:08:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 560, "name": "装置艺术"}, {"id": 4046, "name": "卢森堡"}, {"id": 12672, "name": "秋千"}, {"id": 30362, "name": "Max Mertens"}], "category": 5, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 76, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607192035324EsYkt3lJTHhaxdw.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>当你走上卢森堡市区的商业街<a href=\"http://www.philippe2.lu/2016\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Rue Philippe II</a>，一定会被头顶上悬挂的彩色秋千吸引，每一个秋千的形状一样，排列整齐，都由彩色的绳子悬挂起一块长方形的木板。当风吹过，秋千随意摇晃的时候，就像是看到了彩虹。</p><p class=\"\">彩色秋千布满了这条聚集了各种奢侈品的商业街，无论是购物的人还是坐下来喝咖啡的都会抬头看一看，它们的出现也装点了一种节日的热闹气氛。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607192035590amrgFWAeQ5kiIbX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.988248\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719203557htO4rH1KePomXjVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660256\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607192035587A9pXozhbVjr0yKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660256\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719203558xg7bUvJZ8pyPK4TE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607192035596XIve5CMKcV3osAx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.581250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>这是当地艺术家 <a href=\"http://mmertens.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Max Mertens </a>和卢森堡政府合作的，一共使用了 450 个彩色的木秋千，试图唤起人们一种怀旧的感情和对童年的回忆，吸引更多的人走在秋千之下，“这些秋千都是不能移动的，但它是一种好玩的艺术作品。”Max Mertens 说道。</p><p class=\"\">Rue Philippe II 街道的管理者称“由于城市建设和公交班次的改变，人们越来越少来到市区里，我们需要给他们一个理由，重新走到这些步行区。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719203838EINVfs7AiRTn1Xpy.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607192038380hJSyGcx5gtBisfb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.551667\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">秋千的制作过程，需要将一块长方形木板的四个角打孔，穿上彩色的绳子。</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">这个装置 <a href=\"http://www.philippe2.lu/2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">swings</a> 将维持到 8 月 16 日。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719203949DcYBOt4vEFN9PQjl.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.585455\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">从 2014 年夏天开始，卢森堡政府就在这条街道上做艺术装置来吸引人。当时，他们使用了 <a href=\"http://www.philippe2.lu/2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">1200 把彩色的伞</a>高高悬挂在街道的上空，就是一道明媚的风景。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719204146HRyj83xkNUqAozu6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.532500\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607192041591Sf32CjNIFaiek9P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719204200BFPc6eM7xhSIUYO3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719204530dS0WMUyD9AzJgknv.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553846\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">制作方式是将伞头穿孔挂到绳子上</div></figcaption></figure></div><p>到 2015 年，它们用 6000 根交叉编织的绳子编织了一面蜘蛛网 <a href=\"http://www.philippe2.lu/2015/\" rel=\"nofollow\">look up</a>，这些绳子都是带荧光的彩色，配合着古典式的建筑，像是增加了一股特别的魔力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719204654CErVMv1HDepxWiN0.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563846\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719204823ABw0XEa3KZtIlNmH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719204824mKPReGDlpnOcXx6T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719204824xTEI5UBpysNPruHA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719204841GgBfl0zwFY8ZMEXe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/07/17/video-max-mertens-sky-swings-installation-luxembourg-city-centre-movie/\" rel=\"nofollow\">dezeen</a>、<a href=\"http://mmertens.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Max Mertens</a>、<a href=\"http://www.philippe2.lu/2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rue Philippe II</a></p>"}